6e896158436.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F175708_3ab1c68fd8e491c8fdf316e896158436.jpg&h=dcab68b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電話都有 頂住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電腦嗰隻我而家都有間中玩下"},{"pid":"11b1c0b0225c416e88aa62c5b0844d923234f477","tid":448122,"uid":15867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.rollercoastertycoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/rctd_ss_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollercoastertycoon.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Frctd_ss_03.jpg&h=9c433e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整斷一塊過山車之後全車人一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n困埋同一格路拉高變海再一嘢剷走格路全部浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩完嘔啊嬲啊一嘢吊落海浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd圖毒性好高, planet coaster都比唔到呢隻感覺</blockquote><br />\n有d想買planet coaster,但係咪無career mode?有無人玩過，覺得點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾正<br />\n但d 過山車好難起<br />\n次次都起我粒幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係呢個系列好玩d<br />\n隻planet coaster反而覺得太複雜<br />\nd景點為起而起咁 唔似以前特登執得靚靚仔咁<br />\n而家就係為左升數字啊%啊個d</blockquote><br />\n重一定要2D先最好玩"},{"pid":"f181baad570497ab1c37432f6334a06b8e774b88","tid":448122,"uid":21222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"仙劍客棧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205520d136963b0806b1ebb86f3e0a82b8bf6774","tid":448122,"uid":52418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:11:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f33