"uid":86143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T07:52:02.000Z","msg":"便利商店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8563c91716d557d1e0100bc8a5a82a2d218ae6","tid":448122,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"玩百鬼夜宴識咗好多中國文學同中國歷史 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f64f341397eec59e7afd7410687c7bf25811c7","tid":448122,"uid":18546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有隻舊game係經營黑社會<br />\n<br />\n但唔記得咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑金企業"},{"pid":"0cd86941eb0b042d2eeaa28bb43a65baf9fd2806","tid":448122,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有隻舊game係經營黑社會<br />\n<br />\n但唔記得咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑金企業2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呢隻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7579cfd22022d05cb69a23c40b1606d5d33ed7","tid":448122,"uid":104685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百鬼夜宴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學雞個時屋企未有電腦  去朋友屋企玩呢隻超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好鐘意玩經營遊戲<br />\n個時仲有玩過ps1 唔記得咩名 經營餐廳  細個唔識日文亂玩<br />\n有得自己裝修餐廳同請人  仲可以請外星人打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有PC係附近開鋪搶客  好想玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbce9fff881fda78bf82944021fe331dca035be","tid":448122,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:34:37.000Z","msg":"當初叻人勁人投身創意產業<br />\n日本遊戲發展商生產<br />\n台灣遊戲代理商漢化<br />\n雖然盜版盛行仍然有利可圖<br />\n<br />\n直到網際網路普及免費共享<br />\n個個唔畀錢 公司冇利閏 創作人冇回報<br />\n惡性遁環D game越做越行自然唔及從前好玩"},{"pid":"5efb484e7386dabf70b5ab252138bae8d4793e50","tid":448122,"uid":64398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"天堂島 同 宙斯 都好正"},{"pid":"81fb309ad74083968b9153555506396df5c0235b","tid":448122,"uid":140049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係瘋狂搖搖杯<br />\n十二星座茶屈機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個幾好玩，但真係太易玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b48a377ace9cb40a87cafe33eafcb45822e8ab","tid":448122,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天堂島 同 宙斯 都好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凱撒大帝三無得輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c9bc19d22efe1d9b5ca5ff306bc09d4e9427f6","tid":448122,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"經營快餐店/便利店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c5cbd53875f46a6181fbaf415afb511cb2b679","tid":448122,"uid":39177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:19:42.000Z","msg":"玩咁多年百鬼夜宴都試過睇攻略,完全唔知唔洗開舖果日要做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b1fa2a725325aa85e6c81276294b7d62f31183","tid":448122,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>百鬼夜宴真係世界級<br />\n<br />\n到依家仲擺住係desktop度  <br />\n<br />\n每年都要玩番次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCap張圖黎止下渴，巴打個個有無死機？</blockquote><br />\n李自成入黎會死機既問題 ?  唔知邊度有個補丁down左就可以玩到爆機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92e9d4989895ce31207eea11e1bdfa567429260","tid":448122,"uid":36702,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"百鬼夜宴真係好經典而且內容好豐富既遊戲  <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o2WOHl1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fo2WOHl1.jpg&h=5465b49e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是但開左一個save cap圖     接近爆機<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pbVLaQs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpbVLaQs.jpg&h=6800eb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最強打手<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BOeH1MN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBOeH1MN.jpg&h=e8aca671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次玩好好心次次都借錢比依條慒撚  估唔到最後佢會黎做廚  能力仲好高<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GKhev31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGKhev31.jpg&h=4e66e616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家又係好突然  武功高強會願意黎做小二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zbXZHmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzbXZHmZ.jpg&h=88318eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nd菜色名/做法/賣相都好特別  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2s8haxT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2s8haxT.jpg&h=8b81bbe3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32948f53779f3d13da2eed6d157ca111fa861aed","tid":448122,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"運輸大亨<br />\n電腦重響到未洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacf2a39c4ad08282d7930ba095d31a8d0bb28c0","tid":448122,"uid":17311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:40:43.000Z","msg":"夢幻西餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85afd115ccaa4abf838b0afd797d72f8d818bc6f","tid":448122,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係瘋狂搖搖杯<br />\n十二星座茶屈機</blockquote><br />\n㩒人買嘢飲㩒到mouse都爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a90121bf04b0695f96bc10270076a17697c79f","tid":448122,"uid":51761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百鬼夜宴真係好經典而且內容好豐富既遊戲  <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o2WOHl1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fo2WOHl1.jpg&h=5465b49e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是但開左一個save cap圖     接近爆機<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pbVLaQs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpbVLaQs.jpg&h=6800eb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最強打手<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BOeH1MN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBOeH1MN.jpg&h=e8aca671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次玩好好心次次都借錢比依條慒撚  估唔到最後佢會黎做廚  能力仲好高<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GKhev31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGKhev31.jpg&h=4e66e616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家又係好突然  武功高強會願意黎做小二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zbXZHmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzbXZHmZ.jpg&h=88318eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nd菜色名/做法/賣相都好特別  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2s8haxT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2s8haxT.jpg&h=8b81bbe3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩巴打，好懷念,個個人成日黎借錢，原來會幫你打工真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d135dd2c8935f3b483916274b156aa22872261cd","tid":448122,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.rollercoastertycoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/rctd_ss_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollercoastertycoon.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Frctd_ss_03.jpg&h=9c433e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整斷一塊過山車之後全車人一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n困埋同一格路拉高變海再一嘢剷走格路全部浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩完嘔啊嬲啊一嘢吊落海浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/175708_3ab1c68fd8e491c8fdf316e896158436.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F175708_3ab1c68fd8e491c8fdf316e896158436.jpg&h=dcab68b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電話都有 頂住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電腦嗰隻我而家都有間中玩下</blockquote><br />\n細個一有得玩電腦就會開呢個或者夢幻西餐飲黎玩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得好有成就感 好正 自己中意點設計就點設計<br />\n但過山車自己起好難 通常都會用佢設計好個個<br />\n但有個係360度轉一圈之後向天空衝個個過山車自己可以較去到幾高 有時太高架車會衝出軌道 跌落海/地下 好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲人嘔左出黎之後我會擺返啲人落嘔左個到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住業績好咪會開放新既地圖既<br />\n個陣就會十五十六 開唔開新好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾搬屋 隻碟唔見左 無得玩 出面又買唔到<br />\n試過上網dl 但無得save<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下點樣可以玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4669862dd561ae20c7b57856990295f54fbaacd","tid":448122,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想玩夢幻西餐廳<br />\n如果有MAC版就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無唔係mac版既來源？<br />\n我都好想玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c95f0d77b4ec715ff3cdc6bdc07ff87576a2c0b","tid":448122,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>百鬼夜宴真係好經典而且內容好豐富既遊戲  <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o2WOHl1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fo2WOHl1.jpg&h=5465b49e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是但開左一個save cap圖     接近爆機<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pbVLaQs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpbVLaQs.jpg&h=6800eb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最強打手<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BOeH1MN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBOeH1MN.jpg&h=e8aca671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次玩好好心次次都借錢比依條慒撚  估唔到最後佢會黎做廚  能力仲好高<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GKhev31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGKhev31.jpg&h=4e66e616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家又係好突然  武功高強會願意黎做小二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zbXZHmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzbXZHmZ.jpg&h=88318eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nd菜色名/做法/賣相都好特別  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2s8haxT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2s8haxT.jpg&h=8b81bbe3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩巴打，好懷念,個個人成日黎借錢，原來會幫你打工真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d都係呢隻game吸引既地方"},{"pid":"1b6bb26d0f1bf96bd8df34d3c72311f5fd575cad","tid":448122,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夢幻西餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    以前玩極都上唔到5星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572eb7cebc2c990e7d5946e8c8400738a59c80ef","tid":448122,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:32:37.000Z","msg":"玩過一隻係主角係蒲松齡開餐廳 唔記得叫咩名"},{"pid":"e83cadd842182245f586e405a202a97586a4cb9b","tid":448122,"uid":36444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.rollercoastertycoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/rctd_ss_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollercoastertycoon.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Frctd_ss_03.jpg&h=9c433e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整斷一塊過山車之後全車人一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n困埋同一格路拉高變海再一嘢剷走格路全部浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩完嘔啊嬲啊一嘢吊落海浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/175708_3ab1c68fd8e491c8fdf316e896158436.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F175708_3ab1c68fd8e491c8fdf316e896158436.jpg&h=dcab68b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電話都有 頂住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電腦嗰隻我而家都有間中玩下</blockquote><br />\n細個一</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去steam 有正版賣，50蚊內（忘了價錢<br />\n亦有 rewrite 版本可放大視窗"},{"pid":"3b246c2d5a9148cf84e426ba2fd588a7f7e69061","tid":448122,"uid":144885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:42:20.000Z","msg":"小學玩夢幻遊樂場, 一返去學校就同同學討論殺人方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻game 未試過正常玩 次次都係入去殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232668956a34aa124c85d69be7e0f