faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91cfa6d6ae2b436c61a7d5a5d4761826504ed0d","tid":448122,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"PS 記得有隻模擬便利店<br />\n<br />\n有三個主題，貓、RPG同現代<br />\n<br />\n想搵返黎玩下但唔記得乜名"},{"pid":"a7ac6c6cabc9e99ec08127921a3b90292e6728cc","tid":448122,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"xp年代最好玩梗係創業王"},{"pid":"f9d9e529197b1e38d64022b58d238a3366c1b6b3","tid":448122,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T23:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴絲玩過交通巨人？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n塞車巨人呀<br />\n次次都玩到大塞車<br />\n用d 載10人既車仔頂死對手條線</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高招"},{"pid":"02a9eec77b1d783faf540554561319abae5487f1","tid":448122,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T23:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴絲玩過交通巨人？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n塞車巨人呀<br />\n次次都玩到大塞車<br />\n用d 載10人既車仔頂死對手條線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩到最後，成條街都係自己啲車，zoom遠啲睇剩係見到啲標誌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDOS 年代有隻叫巴士帝國<br />\n玩到依家都過唔到頭幾年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/070424_99fff2fc95a451b223083f0df37a68fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F070424_99fff2fc95a451b223083f0df37a68fe.jpg&h=024a7eb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6ba126a59016d941e06021dd92e42d25f2b14b4","tid":448122,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學玩夢幻遊樂場, 一返去學校就同同學討論殺人方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻game 未試過正常玩 次次都係入去殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過山車殺人同吊啲人落去遊下水唔係應該要做嘅嘢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆街去到第三集竟然cut哂啲殺人方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7a3d806ba1800149bcf130701ec69a9bbaf89e","tid":448122,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"好like maxis 嘅sim game<br />\nSim park sim farm sim tower sim city <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n杏林醫院後面難到仆街 <br />\n成日地震 又有傳染病 <br />\n  <br />\n其實我果個年代已經無人玩呢d game 但我偏偏好鍾意揾番老豆 d 舊game 碟嚟玩 <br />\n開個dos 模擬器玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見咁多巴打玩過咁多dos game 想離題一問 好細過果陣玩過一隻恐怖類game<br />\n一開初個天好黑 眼前有一間屋 要係地墊底下揾到條key 開完之後 有一間房有張bb床 要揾奶餵佢 之後去雪櫃入面攞完現成嘅奶樽<br />\n就係呢個時候 係穿咗洞嘅牆見到有人將bb攞走 然後從時空門離開 好似diablo 嘅town scroll <br />\n之後跟埋入去 見到有個成年人伏係床上 無知覺 然後鏡頭一轉 被打暈咗<br />\n講到一舊舊 唔知有無巴打知道係咩game 揾咗好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71468fcdfd0fc6c0f5d9d3548ecc244d346d3451","tid":448122,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadd5d7e8f7892cbf4cfb46027519b735588b14a","tid":448122,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"百鬼夜宴真心正<br />\n啲bgm 又好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好鍾意龜<br />\n次次都請隻掌櫃同廚師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}